title: For Sale/Trade:  Norinco MAK 90  AK47
postcontent: Norinco MAK 90.  All Chinese.  Original Blued finish. Excellent condition.  Looking for offers for quality items. Cash offers welcome.  I have the original thumbhole stock as well.  Comes with 3 chinese flatback nags, 2 pmags and 1 european mag. Gun has now been updated with correct 14x1 LH threading for barrel. Please make reasonable trade offers. This is not a $600 WASR.  I am not going to trade for your Grandpa's 870, Mom's sewing machine or your brand new HiPoint.  This is a collector grade PreBan AK 47.  Manufactured in 1993 before the Federal AWB. 100% Chinese. There 2 types of Pre Ban guns as there was 2 different bans. Pre 1994 AWB and pre 1989 section 922r compliance guns.  Some states adopted the Federal AWB. This gun would be legal to add folding/collaspable stocks and forward grips and other features to in those states like Conneticut. Additionally a limited number of Pre 89 Norinco guns were marked MAk 90. Those will not have a year at the start of the serial number.  This is not one of those limited guns. This one has 93 as the first 2 digits to designate it was produced in 1993.
